{"word":"ἐμαυτοῦ","slug":"ἐμαυτοῦ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐμαυτοῦ, ῆς</el></b> [<el>ἐμοῦ, αὐτού</el>] reflexive first <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pron.\">pron.</a>, only in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a>, and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sg.\">sg.</a> <b>myself<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a>, possessive <b><a href='B:530 10:33'>1 Cor 10:33</a>;</b> <el>ἄπ</el>’/<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐξ\">ἐξ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐμαυτοῦ\">ἐμαυτοῦ</a></el> on my own authority/volition <b><a href='B:500 5:30'>J 5:30</a>; <a href='B:500 7:17'>7:17</a>; <a href='B:500 8:42'>8:42</a>; <a href='B:500 12:49'>12:49</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a> <b><a href='B:510 20:24'>Ac 20:24</a>; <a href='B:520 11:4'>Ro 11:4</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔδοξα\">ἔδοξα</a> ἐμαυτῷ</el> I was convinced <b><a href='B:510 26:9'>Ac 26:9</a>;</b> <el>σύνοιδά τι ἐμαυτῷ</el> I am conscious of <b><a href='B:530 4:4'>1 Cor 4:4</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a>, simply <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> verb <b><a href='B:490 7:7'>Lk 7:7</a>;</b> <el>ὑπ</el>’ <el>ἐμαυτόν</el> under my authority <b><a href='B:470 8:9'>Mt 8:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔμαθον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐμβαίνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}